Package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.factory

Class ComponentFactory

java.lang.Object
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.factory.ComponentFactory
public class ComponentFactory extends Object
Factory class responsible for dynamically creating UI component instances.

This class retrieves component instances based on their type using reflection. It scans the project package and framework package for implementations of UI components that are annotated with ImplementationOfType.
